<item>
            <title>[HBASE-11078] [AccessController] Consider new permission for &quot;read visible&quot;</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-11078</link>
                <project id="12310753" key="HBASE">HBase</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;See parent for the whole story.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Consider a new permission with the semantics &quot;being able to read only granted cells&quot;, perhaps called READ_VISIBLE. &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Maybe consider a symmetric new permission for writes. &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The lack of default READ perm should prevent users from launching scanners.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
